{"tid":1827041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反中派肯坐低傾地區直選出邊23條飛未","createTime":"2020-01-16T15:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T22:48:38.000Z","uid":210495,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e4e5fd60e848ba13c9743b49a5fdd0d2ba819e","tid":1827041,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"既然傳統民主派唔會主辦出擊2020立法會全面直選，又已經開始黨內初選，係咪係時候所有泛民＋本土坐低傾下地區直選出邊23條飛<br />\n2020唔全面直選，都要立法會議席過半＋功能組別過半<br />\n<blockquote>最多議席數目：假設建制派以進取策略在各區派出候選名單，以這些數據可推算出反政府陣營在各區能取得的最多議席數目分別是：港島4席、九東3席、九西4席、新東7席、新西6席，共24席。 &mdash;&mdash;<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191203/OTIQD74MQJLZXQOUDXL5KMXSAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191203%2FOTIQD74MQJLZXQOUDXL5KMXSAM%2F&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=b7ba291e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191203%2FOTIQD74MQJLZXQOUDXL5KMXSAM%2F&h=7d3ba029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191203/OTIQD74MQJLZXQOUDXL5KMXSAM/</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n民主黨七名現任立法會議員角逐下屆連任<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eLskuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eLskuS</a><br />\n公民黨新生代抬頭 余德寶、鄭達鴻擬戰立法會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1825983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1825983</a>"},{"pid":"b96bdbe5dbf7ffc0dc0b59a2a40237144c37d680","tid":1827041,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T15:46:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">歐美議員講野又無人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響task2呀 幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif